{"tid":257062,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲92歲廢老娶了107位老婆：「這是上天旨意」","createTime":"2017-05-25T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T18:01:39.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9578d0ce2340fcf3e891c0891616e5a39c60281a","tid":257062,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161021/972292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161021%2F972292%2F&d=1hWmPSacJKZtYHxjwETg5TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=aa0c8b33\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161021/972292/</a><br />\n《鹿鼎記》中的韋小寶娶了7個老婆不夠看，奈及利亞一名92歲老翁阿布巴卡(Mohammed Bello Abubakar)，就娶了107位老婆，之後陸續休掉10位，目前也有97位老婆，而阿布巴卡就說：「這都是上天旨意。」<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，阿布巴卡的「事蹟」最早在2008年被報導出來，因為當時執法機關要求他放棄大多數老婆，但阿布巴卡回說：「我要活到老、娶到老，直到死亡的那一刻。」不過最近阿布巴卡再度接受訪問時改口說「兩個老婆就夠了」，但他還是堅稱自己擁有這麼多老婆，都是「上天旨意」，而他會繼續完成老天爺給的指示，直到生命盡頭。有伊斯蘭教長老批評阿布巴卡，說他違反「4個老婆」的伊斯蘭教教義。但阿布巴卡回應，說批評他的人完全是在「嫉妒」老天賦予他娶老婆的任務。就有台灣網友神計算：「平均3個月才能輪完一圈。」還有網友說：「我想請他背誦出，所有老婆的姓名和生日。」還有網友質疑：「他的身體受得了嗎？」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"95ba9604a7cbe7b96e3f8d914c6a91b183932360","tid":257062,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"應該有好多頂綠帽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b0b89013771626eb34357f4423923585007ecd","tid":257062,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"生左203個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ea23280b5bdd533a131d0fbc4b7039e96a8c5e","tid":257062,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"點養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14c07957f32c75ae9e03740e15a21aa13320c19","tid":257062,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>（<span style=\"color: red;\">施旖婕</span>／綜合外電報導）</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b621eea2ed100cc1f7853a10ccc8a5cf4b306a4","tid":257062,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}